meta_keyword: RADIANS SV225-2ZGM-2X 2XL HI VIZ GREEN MESH VEST CLASS 2 SELF EXTINGUI

meta_title: RADIANS SV25-2ZGM-4XL 4X FR CLASS II VEST W/ZIPPER CLOSURE
summary: Fire Retardant (NFPA 701 Treated Fabric) standard class 2 safety vest. Made with 100% polyester mesh and two tone trim. Non-durable FR protection is achieved by chemically treating a material that is not naturally fire retardant, but becomes self-extinguishing after the treatment.
meta_keyword: RADIANS SV25-2ZGM-4XL 4X FR CLASS II VEST W/ZIPPER CLOSURE

meta_keyword: RADIANS SV25-2ZGM-M MEDIUM FR CLASS II VEST WITH ZIPPER CLOSURE

Protect your face and neck from cold, harsh elements with Nordic Blaze® Warming Gear by Radians.  The RWL22SE is a versatile three-in-one ergonomic design that is made with Nordic thermal fleece for added warmth and comfort.  It easily converts from balaclava to a neck gator or face shield offering you different levels of protection for changing weather conditions.

meta_title: Nordic Blaze® Dual Layer Shoulder Length Thermal Hard Hat Liner
short_description: Protect your head and neck from cold, harsh elements with thermal Nordic Blaze® Warming Gear by Radians.  The RWL17 is an ergonomically designed dual layer, shoulder length hard hat liner.  It has a hook and loop closure that easily attaches to your internal hard hat system.  The quilted outer layer blocks out chilly weather and the inner Nordic fleece thermal layer keeps in heat.
meta_keyword: Nordic Blaze® Dual Layer Shoulder Length Thermal Hard Hat Liner

meta_title: Nordic Blaze® Thermal Hard Hat Liner
short_description: Protect your head and neck from cold, harsh elements with thermal Nordic Blaze® Warming Gear by Radians.  The RWL19 is a lightweight ergonomically designed hard hat liner.  It has a hook and loop closure that easily attaches to your internal hard hat system and a chin strap that provides stability while wearing hard hats.  It has an outer layer to block out wind and an inner Nordic fleece thermal layer to keep in heat.
meta_keyword: Nordic Blaze® Thermal Hard Hat Liner

meta_title: Lens Cleaning Towelettes - 100 Count - in Box
short_description: Sturdy, economical lens cleaning accessories provide instant access for all lens cleaning needs in the plant or office. Strategically placed stations will promote proper lens cleaning techniques extending the life of prescription and non-prescription safety glasses. The specially developed formula in the lens cleaning towelettes and lens cleaning stations will clean greasy and oily glasses while providing an anti-fog / anti-static coating. Low lint, non-abrasive tissue leaves lenses clear and streak free. Cleaning wipes for Respirators are also available in an alcohol free option.
meta_keyword: Lens Cleaning Towelettes - 100 Count - in Box

Radians SV75B Surveyor Type R Class 2 Self-Extinguishing Safety Vest features a black bottom, two Mic Tabs and a zipper closure.? The SV75B has five pockets, including a radio pocket, upper split pocket with pencil pockets, lower front covered pockets and a rear plan pocket. This garment is made from polyester treated to be self-extinguishing as defined by ASTM D6413 (< 2.0s flameout / < 6" char length). This garment should never be used where an arc flash or flash fire hazard is present.

This garment is made from polyester treated to be self-extinguishing as defined by ASTM D6413 (< 2.0s flameout / < 6" char length). This garment should never be used where an arc flash or flash fire hazard is present.

Radians DURARAD™ 42, acid gear waterproof rainwear, will keep workers dry in the rain or provide protection from dirty working conditions. The heavy duty PVC/Poly material provides excellent protection in hazardous conditions which require extra performance, yet is soft and flexible for comfort. The treated polyester is Self-Extinguishing (SE) to test method D6413. The DURARAD™ 42 series rainwear includes a jacket, bib overalls, and full length coveralls, all sold separately.  Applications: Petrochemical, Chemical Applications, Environmental Clean-Up.

Radians SV45-2 Economy Type R Class 2 Self-Extinguishing breakaway vest with 3 Pockets.  Garment is made from polyester treated to be self-extinguishing as defined by ASTM D6413 (< 2.0s flameout / < 6" char length).  This garment should never be used where an arc flash or flash fire hazard is present.  Typical applications would be Ship Building, Steel Erection, Bridge Building, Fabrication, Asphalt Paving, and other applications involving FR hazards that result from errant sparks rather than open circuit electricity or a potentially explosive atmosphere.
